# Cover Image Suggestions for "Reduce Customer Churn with Perspective AI"

1. A visual metaphor showing a customer journey path with multiple "exit points" being blocked or redirected by proactive retention strategies. Use a clean, modern design with clear visual flow.

2. A split-screen showing the contrast between reactive churn management (empty seats, lost customers) and proactive retention (engaged customers, growth). Use contrasting colors and clear visual hierarchy.

3. An abstract visualization of customer retention as a protective shield or safety net, with customers being supported and guided through their journey. The design should use warm, supportive colors and convey security and stability. 